/-- Recursor for free semigroup using `of` and `*`. -/
@[to_additive (attr := elab_as_elim) "Recursor for free additive semigroup using `of` and `+`."]
protected def recOnMul {C : FreeSemigroup α → Sort l} (x) (ih1 : ∀ x, C (of x))
